992
00:57:21,605 --> 00:57:24,206
Si me amas, como dices...

993
00:57:25,009 --> 00:57:27,643
Tú eres la única.

994
00:57:28,913 --> 00:57:30,913
Oh...

995
00:57:33,751 --> 00:57:36,118
Tú y John Amos.

996
00:57:37,655 --> 00:57:40,456
¿John Amos?

997
00:57:40,458 --> 00:57:43,659
